{"tid":2259561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"信報：藍絲kol拍片推介藍店 / 分析指預算案有機會押後","createTime":"2020-10-27T02:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T03:02:10.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac7c8fb0cbe3c9650d2084061b9854ce3aceeb76","tid":2259561,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:31:59.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯除了「轉場」，這班KOL亦積極「轉型」以維持人氣，因為新冠疫情肆虐令政治及示威活動轉趨淡靜，可用作輿論戰的「彈藥」或「炮台」買少見少。其中發起「KOL 100」計劃的李梓敬近日有新搞作，與多名於建制陣營略有名氣的網紅開設新的政治娛樂頻道，向網民軟銷「藍店」食肆及商品等，已累積逾3萬訂閱。他們稍後擬開設「藍營」網店賣撐警產品，又會組織類似菁英會性質的青年政治團體，推廣政治論述。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2616310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2616310&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=ddab444f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2616310</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⋯可惜言猶在耳，因中共第十九屆五中全會下周一至周四在北京舉行，消息指林鄭在此段時間未能獲安排上京，意味港府月內率團赴京的機會極微。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭於本月12日宣布推遲宣讀《施政報告》，當時她言之鑿鑿表示月內上京，外界都以為一切準備就緒，只欠「北風」。豈料一個多星期過去，特首仍未啟程，到周五更傳出延後，看來又再「甩拖」。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯ 事實上，除了市民大眾關心《施政報告》能否如期發表外，一眾官員更加憂心忡忡，事關財政司司長明年2月發表新一份《財政預算案》，按照傳統，預算案公布前大半年，政府已開始內部資源分配工作（Resources Allocation Exercise，RAE），審視各政策措施，以決定各部門的預算。<br />\n<br />\n如今《施政報告》推遲個多月公布，RAE進度必然落後，加上12月底又遇上聖誕節長假期，近日不少政府中人開始猜測會否出現骨牌效應，導致預算案亦要一併押後。<br />\n<br />\n有添馬中人提醒筆者，過去兩年，預算案都在12月開始諮詢，如果今年底前財爺還未有動作，或許已露端倪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2615534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2615534&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=350be0dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2615534</a>"},{"pid":"355b396123bea6e363ae45e8f70b5cb568b3d09b","tid":2259561,"uid":77717,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:34:44.000Z","msg":"賣撐警產品，食人血饅頭，你班人推啊蛇去死自己cap水，對唔對得着受傷啊蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8c2a9e06949cee32a52191db04640de163c6dc","tid":2259561,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:38:10.000Z","msg":"叫人血專家光時P 做搞手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncap 完黃cap 埋藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n收益全數捐比受傷賤賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2514896a353c5133aa166289cedcdfbbb6f5dc","tid":2259561,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:40:22.000Z","msg":"咁咪岩，大家各自各幫襯"},{"pid":"9935900bce2c4c1eb043e579daa6957f5940d55a","tid":2259561,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"355b396123bea6e363ae45e8f70b5cb568b3d09b","tid":2259561,"uid":77717,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:34:44.000Z","msg":"賣撐警產品，食人血饅頭，你班人推啊蛇去死自己cap水，對唔對得着受傷啊蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"食藍店當撐警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568b426827da20f54f712b620ba078c050ccff77","tid":2259561,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:44:31.000Z","msg":"難得有個list可以抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好店門口有撐共貼紙"},{"pid":"ca3b4a12ba2c1eecf873df0833fda2c2a477f95a","tid":2259561,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"3萬訂閱..笑死~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n周庭BB 搞個YT channel 搞左幾個月都十萬啦(好似係)"},{"pid":"47e1c7b7e7c63f7337551aa05cae4cbbfcb82099","tid":2259561,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca3b4a12ba2c1eecf873df0833fda2c2a477f95a","tid":2259561,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,